oleBinding)\n- `templates/_helpers.tpl` (ServiceAccount name helpers)\n\n**Configuration:**\n- `values.yaml` - Complete RBAC configuration structure\n\n### RBAC Architecture\n\n| Component | ServiceAccount | Role/ClusterRole | Scope | Permissions |\n|-----------|---------------|------------------|-------|-------------|\n| controller-manager | `agentcube` | Role | Namespace | Custom rules (empty by default) |\n| workload-manager | `agentcube-workload-manager` | ClusterRole | Cluster | CRDs, pods, services, configmaps, secrets, events |\n| router | `agentcube-router` | Role | Namespace | Secrets (get, list, watch) |\n\n### Verification\n\n✅ Helm templates render correctly  \n✅ All RBAC resources created (3 SAs, 2 Roles, 1 ClusterRole, 2 RoleBindings, 1 ClusterRoleBinding)  \n✅ ServiceAccounts follow naming convention  \n✅ RBAC resources have correct labels  \n✅ Permissions match design specification  \n✅ All acceptance criteria met","time":{"start":1775882589452,"end":1775882589452}}}
